{"tid":1515022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰更新員工守則　鼓勵舉報違反守則情況","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:57:17.000Z","uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"e0cb2d9f836c499fc529720be4d711f631cb7111","tid":1515022,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"文革咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=360861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360861&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=899be512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360861&h=81061ec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=360861</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CATHAY-MEMO-190829-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCATHAY-MEMO-190829-11.jpg&h=4751f69a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空更新員工行為守則，表明對員工參與非法活動會採取零容忍的態度，又鼓勵員工舉報任何懷疑違反守則的情況。<br />\n<br />\n國泰向員工發內部通告，指近日有關解僱員工的報道中有很多錯誤資訊，令員工感到焦慮，公司不會評論個別個案，但向員工保證，解僱決定是經過高層正式及謹慎檢視。國泰對員工參與非法活動會採取零容忍的態度，亦不容許員工使用公司資源表達政治意見。<br />\n<br />\n通告指出，公司需要建立服從的文化，因此鼓勵員工舉報身邊任何懷疑違反守則的情況，公司會跟進調查並保護舉報人的身分。"},{"pid":"d05b63e7cae9a3f0a9d08f4ff1f37d97b6d959e4","tid":1515022,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1981b05536e9cb0016b61af96e0d1f1fdf965d1b","tid":1515022,"uid":267172,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"再講咩罷工會比人炒嘅話<br />\n無人會幫到你地班國泰員工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地對唔對得住手足斷左嘅手足 無左嘅視力 死左嘅生命 即將失去嘅未來</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea307aae08dab64214fc20700109a1550f894109","tid":1515022,"uid":202464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國泰工會仍然選擇沉默。</span>"},{"pid":"59d406b92d17163dfa7664141d5bb623365bc9d3","tid":1515022,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"國泰城<br />\n<br />\n國泰城<br />\n<br />\n國泰城"},{"pid":"6042cd7dcbc498f13f50f923c0c35eec7b44908f","tid":1515022,"uid":122179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司"},{"pid":"61d5997cdefa181f0e52e9dbf7dea69bf8b1b06d","tid":1515022,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07d761fb8829f19e7404c463fc017f08920e194","tid":1515022,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"乜撚野服從文化呀"},{"pid":"ded33813ffab18c53d4758320862c986bc311530","tid":1515022,"uid":124473,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b07d761fb8829f19e7404c463fc017f08920e194","tid":1515022,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"乜撚野服從文化呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"轉左CEO後仲叫人撐CX既麻煩出黎講幾句"},{"pid":"f35dcdd367d8b4dd1c8f49e9ebd16dd290c692f6","tid":1515022,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<br />\n個公會都係垃圾，淨係叫加人工先走出來"},{"pid":"9bda9c303fd264939410bf99ed8c4563b37f5e56","tid":1515022,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"轉咗紅底仲要撐？玩埋文革"},{"pid":"7f5a7c1a400fce7f2b2aa6407686b2094e28d74a","tid":15150